This is an unofficial third-party Electron wrapper for the Apple Music web
player at https://music.apple.com/. It is not endorsed by, sponsored by, or
affiliated with Apple Inc. Apple, Apple Music, and the Apple Music logo are
trademarks of Apple Inc.

The Apple Music icon is derived from Apple's publicly served web-player
favicon at https://music.apple.com/assets/favicon/favicon-180.png and is used
only to identify the service opened by this wrapper. This repository contains
no Apple application code or media. Use of Apple Music remains subject to
Apple's applicable terms and privacy policy.

This project uses Castlabs Electron for Content Security, an MIT-licensed fork
of Electron that enables dynamic installation of Google's proprietary Widevine
Content Decryption Module. Widevine is downloaded from Google only after user
consent and is not redistributed by this repository or its release artifacts.
Google and Widevine are trademarks of Google LLC.
